parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the timing chain tensioner can cause the timing chain to malfunction, leading to engine damage, loss of proper timing, and potentially causing accidents.
The oil leak can cause the engine to lose oil, leading to engine damage and potentially causing accidents.
The burning odor and engine issues can cause discomfort and potentially lead to accidents.
The exhaust system issues can cause fume odors to enter the vehicle, making the driver sick and potentially leading to accidents.
The general vehicle problems can cause discomfort, inconvenience, and potentially lead to accidents.

the vehicle is unable to stop accelerating without shutting off the engine.
